'''崔瑞元'''（{{kor|최서원}}，{{bd|1956年|6月23日}}），原名'''崔順實'''（{{kor|최순실}}），[[韓國|韓國]]人士，為前[[韓國總統|韓國總統]][[朴槿惠|朴槿惠]]的好友兼親信。她是[[2016年韓國政治醜聞|2016年韓國政治醜聞]]主要人物，涉及干政及操弄大權。

==經歷==
她是第十八任[[韓國總統|韓國總統]][[朴槿惠|朴槿惠]]涉及的[[2016年韓國政治醜聞|2016年韓國政治醜聞]]的主要人物<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/28/world/asia/south-korea-choi-soon-sil.html?_r=0|title=A Presidential Friendship Has Many South Koreans Crying Foul|date=October 27, 2016|website=New York Times|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2016-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161211102435/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/28/world/asia/south-korea-choi-soon-sil.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://qz.com/821612/a-rasputinesque-mystery-woman-and-a-cultish-religion-could-take-down-south-koreas-president-park-geun-hye/|date=October 28, 2016|title=A Rasputinesque mystery woman and a cultish religion could take down South Korea’s president|website=Quartz|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122001709/http://qz.com/821612/a-rasputinesque-mystery-woman-and-a-cultish-religion-could-take-down-south-koreas-president-park-geun-hye/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/767405.html|date=October 26, 2016|title=‘It’s actually a system where Choi Sun-sil tells the President what to do’|website=The Hankyoreh|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2017-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170104015724/http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/767405.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/10/116_216623.html|date=October 23, 2016|title=Investigations into 'Choi Soon-sil gate' widening|website=The Korea Times|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113121620/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/10/116_216623.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Key suspects still at large in Choi Sun-sil probe|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3025312|accessdate=2016-10-29|date=October 25, 2016|website=韩国中央日报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108012749/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=3025312|archive-date=2016-11-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。她被控涉嫌干預總統朴槿惠制定政府政策和決定，包括在未有官職的情況下得以閱讀國家情報及南韓機密<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20161025000359|title=Presidential speeches found on confidante’s PC: report|date=October 25, 2016|website=The Korea Herald|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729133706/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20161025000359|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/south-koreas-presidency-on-the-brink-of-collapse-as-scandal-grows/2016/10/28/7639a2cc-1700-4ef7-a3a4-661b3ff989c4_story.html|title=South Korea’s presidency ‘on the brink of collapse’ as scandal grows|date=October 29, 2016|website=Washington Post|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2018-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201151457/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/south-koreas-presidency-on-the-brink-of-collapse-as-scandal-grows/2016/10/28/7639a2cc-1700-4ef7-a3a4-661b3ff989c4_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Can Pres. Park be investigated over Choi Sun-sil scandal?|url=http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/767846.html|accessdate=2016-10-29|date=October 28, 2016|website=[[韓民族日報|韓民族日報]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171208003941/http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/767846.html|archive-date=2017-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/troubling-revelations-about-seouls-shadow-president-the-korea-herald-columnist|title=Troubling revelations about Seoul's 'Shadow President': The Korea Herald columnist|date=October 27, 2016|website=[[海峽時報|海峽時報]]|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2017-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171208011824/http://www.straitstimes.com/asia/east-asia/troubling-revelations-about-seouls-shadow-president-the-korea-herald-columnist|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=‘Choi-gate’ scandal snowballing|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3025234|accessdate=2016-10-29|date=October 22, 2016|website=韩国中央日报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230230121/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aId=3025234|archive-date=2017-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/south-koreas-leader-acknowledges-ties-to-woman-in-scandal/2016/10/25/def52790-9a91-11e6-b552-b1f85e484086_story.html|title=South Korea’s leader acknowledges ties to woman in scandal|date=October 25, 2016|website=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216223319/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/south-koreas-leader-acknowledges-ties-to-woman-in-scandal/2016/10/25/def52790-9a91-11e6-b552-b1f85e484086_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 家庭 ==
其父親[[崔太敏|崔太敏]]自創[[新興宗教|新興宗教]]，稱[[永世教|永世教]]。

[[鄭潤會|鄭潤會]]為崔順實前夫，1995年結婚，已於2014年離婚。[[郑维罗|郑维罗]]是她和前夫的女兒<ref>{{cite news|last=Kim|first=Oi-hyun|title=Pres. Park's former aide and his wife may be at the center of ongoing scandal|url=http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/667320.html|date=December 3, 2014|newspaper=[[韓民族日報|韓民族日報]]|access-date=23 September 2016|archive-date=2017-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928072635/http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/667320.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite news |last=Park |first=Sojung |title=S. Korea wins gold in team dressage equestrian at Asiad |url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/topic/2014/09/20/90/1350010000AEN20140920003001315F.html |date=September 20, 2014 |newspaper=[[Yonhap|Yonhap]] |access-date=23 September 2016 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220072216/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/topic/2014/09/20/90/1350010000AEN20140920003001315F.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因為被[[梨花女子大学|梨花女子大学]]违例破格录取，产生大量争议<ref name="#2">{{cite news|last1=姜|first1=贵瑛|title=被指违例让总统亲友女儿入学 韩梨花女大校长辞职|url=http://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/international/story20161020-679917|accessdate=2016-11-01|publisher=联合早报|date=2016-10-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101103141/http://www.zaobao.com.sg/znews/international/story20161020-679917|archivedate=2016-11-01|language=zh}}</ref>。

==爭議==
=== 干政醜聞 ===
2016年10月下旬，檢察官突擊搜查崔順實的辦公室和住宅<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/south-korea-s-president-accused-of-leaking-classified-documents/3237900.html|title=South Korea's president accused of leaking classified documents|date=October 26, 2016|website=Channel NewsAsia|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027145341/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/south-korea-s-president-accused-of-leaking-classified-documents/3237900.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/10/116_216947.html|title=Long hide-and-seek game begins for Choi Soon-sil|date=October 27, 2016|website=The Korea Times|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825191736/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/10/116_216947.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其後朴槿惠的秘書在醜聞公開後遭勒令辭職<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/10/116_217058.html|title=Park orders secretaries to resign over 'Choi Soon-sil scandal'|date=October 28, 2016|website=The Korea Times|accessdate=2016-10-29|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730120502/https://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/nation/2016/10/116_217058.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前，她可能曾命令韓國檢察官起訴日本記者[[加藤達也_(記者)|加藤達也]]，指他誹謗朴槿惠和前任幕僚長[[鄭潤會|鄭潤會]]（崔順實前夫）於[[世越号沉没事故|世越号沉没事故]]同崔順實秘密會面七小時<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gale|first1=Alastair|title=Korean Prosecutors Indict Japanese Journalist on Defamation Charge|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/korean-prosecutors-indict-japanese-journalist-on-defamation-charge-1412826990|accessdate=2016-10-30|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=2014-10-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030000139/http://www.wsj.com/articles/korean-prosecutors-indict-japanese-journalist-on-defamation-charge-1412826990|archivedate=2016-10-30|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=朴槿惠就亲信审阅总统演讲稿一事向国民道歉|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-10/27/c_129338581.htm|accessdate=2016-10-30|agency=新华社|date=2016-10-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030050724/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-10/27/c_129338581.htm|archivedate=2016-10-30|language=zh-cn}}</ref>。到10月29日時，[[首爾|首爾]][[清溪川|清溪川]]廣場有過萬名民眾[[2016年韩国示威|集會]]，要求朴槿惠下台及羈押崔順實，[[正义党_(韩国)|正義黨]][[韓國國會|國會議員]][[魯會燦|魯會燦]]和民主運動家{{link-ko|白基玩|백기완}}均有參與<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201610290290-1.aspx |title=崔順實干政 逾萬民眾聚集要朴槿惠下台 |accessdate=2016-10-29 |archive-date=2017-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401122401/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201610290290-1.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年10月29日回國，於11月1日受拘押，11月3日正式遭到逮捕，11月19日正式起訴。事件導致朴槿惠被國會彈劾，最終被罷免。2018年2月13日，首爾中央地方法院以包括濫用權力、欺詐未遂及強迫等裁定崔順實罪名成立，判監20年。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=992863&csid=261_367|title=崔順實一審判監20年有13項控罪與朴槿惠共謀|date=2018-02-13|work=商業電台即時新聞|accessdate=2018-02-13|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404044145/https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=992863&csid=261_367|dead-url=yes}}</ref>8月24日，在二审中，[[朴槿惠|朴槿惠]]被判25年，崔顺实本人被判20年<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://biz.heraldcorp.com/culture/view.php?ud=201808241623505712861_1|title=최순실 징역 20년, 출소하면 ‘85세’…변호인 뜬금 '궁예' 발언 왜?|publisher=헤럴드경제|date=2018-08-24|accessdate=2018-08-24|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120000526/http://biz.heraldcorp.com/culture/view.php?ud=201808241623505712861_1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 滥用特權 ===
馬術「[[盛裝舞步|盛裝舞步]]」運動員[[郑维罗|郑维罗]]是她和前夫的女兒<ref>{{cite news |last=Kim |first=Oi-hyun |title=Pres. Park's former aide and his wife may be at the center of ongoing scandal |url=http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/667320.html |date=December 3, 2014 |newspaper=The Hankyoreh |access-date=23 September 2016 |archive-date=2017-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928072635/http://english.hani.co.kr/arti/english_edition/e_national/667320.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/>，因為被名校[[梨花女子大学|梨花女子大学]]录取，产生大量争议<ref name="#2"/>，梨大師生曾為此[[2016年梨花女子大學示威|示威]]數十日，最終迫使校長引咎下台。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://udn.com/news/story/6809/2052596 |title=朴槿惠閨密風暴！認了干政 |accessdate=2016-11-03 |archive-date=2016-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113004119/http://udn.com/news/story/6809/2052596 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其女兒進入梨大後經常以不符要求的理由曠課，校方卻許可；鄭在部分科目不交作業、不參加考試，校方也讓她過關，甚至有教授代替她交作業。南韓教育部基於上述結果，將要求梨大取消其的入學資格，但其已於2016年10月31日透過網路申請退學，因此梨大無法直接開除其入學資格。

2016年11月15日，韓國教育部對其女兒發布的報告指出，她在[[清潭高中|清潭高中]]不但高三僅上課17天還能畢業，且超額參與運動賽事（一年只能參加4次），因此要求該高中取消其畢業證書。<ref name="청담">[http://m.hani.co.kr/arti/society/society_general/766981.html#cb 단독 정유라 고3때 131일 결석…승마협회 공문 덕에 모두 ‘공결’] {{Wayback|url=http://m.hani.co.kr/arti/society/society_general/766981.html#cb |date=20161120084542 }}한겨레. 2016년 10월 24일에 확인함.</ref>同時也要求[[梨花女子大學|梨花女子大學]]取消她的入學資格，並追究相關人士。

2017年6月23日，[[首爾中央地方法院|首爾中央地方法院]]以妨礙業務裁定崔順實罪名成立，判監3年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170623/mobile/bknint-20170623094346343-0623_17011_001.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-06-23 |archive-date=2020-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404044201/https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170623/mobile/bknint-20170623094346343-0623_17011_001.html }}</ref>。11月14日，{{ko-link|首尔高等法院|서울고등법원}}进行二审宣判，崔顺实因帮助女儿入学舞弊被判处3年有期徒刑<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2017-11-14/1161330.html |title=朴槿惠闺蜜崔顺实二审被判3年 前梨大校长被判2年 |access-date=2019-08-29 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119234024/http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2017-11-14/1161330.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年8月29日下午2时，[[韩国最高法院|韩国最高法院]]推翻崔顺实二审判决，将案件发回{{ko-link|首尔高等法院|서울고등법원}}重审<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2019/08-29/8941271.shtml |title=发回重审！四年了，朴槿惠“亲信干政案”还未完结…… |access-date=2019-08-29 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119234029/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2019/08-29/8941271.shtml }}</ref>。

2020年6月11日上午，[[韩国最高法院|韩国最高法院]]作出终审判决，以“滥用职权、妨害行使权力”“诈骗未遂”等罪名判处崔顺实18年有期徒刑，罚款200亿[[韩元|韩元]]，追缴犯罪所得63亿韩元<ref>{{cite news |title=崔顺实获刑18年，但“亲信干政案”仍未落幕 |url=http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202006/11/WS5ee1a90fe4b00aba04d212a1.html |accessdate=2020-06-11 |archive-date=2020-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701054547/http://www.bjd.com.cn/a/202006/11/WS5ee1a90fe4b00aba04d212a1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

